title: Manchester United boss Louis van Gaal 'sick' of questions about Wayne Rooney - Andover Advertiser
text:
Louis van Gaal said he was "sick" of answering questions about Wayne Rooney's form following a dull and goalless Manchester derby. Jesse Lingard rattled the bar and Chris Smalling drew a late save from Joe Hart, but otherwise the hosts rarely looked like getting the breakthrough against a defensive-minded City side.
 Andover Advertiser.
